02:05:16.160 --> 02:05:18.840
But in the meantime, Inositol does seem

02:05:18.840 --> 02:05:22.560
to have some positive effects on anxiety.

02:05:22.560 --> 02:05:26.200
And therefore it might
provide a kind of supportive

02:05:26.200 --> 02:05:28.410
indirect effect for people that are trying

02:05:28.410 --> 02:05:31.330
to work through trauma and PTSD.

02:05:31.330 --> 02:05:32.870
Now, the question is
