02:05:50.450 --> 02:05:53.230
Because if you put a drug
or a compound of any kind

02:05:53.230 --> 02:05:56.220
prescription drug or
supplement or any kind

02:05:56.220 --> 02:06:00.450
into your system you are
essentially short-circuiting

02:06:00.450 --> 02:06:04.010
