02:09:04.970 --> 02:09:06.680
You'll see evidence of 50 milligrams,

02:09:06.680 --> 02:09:07.753
you'll see evidence of 300 milligrams,

02:09:07.753 --> 02:09:09.780
is kind of all over the place.

02:09:09.780 --> 02:09:12.770
But each of these studies
alone and together

02:09:12.770 --> 02:09:15.770
point to the fact that
Kava does seem to produce

02:09:15.770 --> 02:09:20.770
a very potent anxiolytic and
general kind of improvement

02:09:21.400 --> 02:09:26.070
